  <Summary>Mechanics Parts 1 to 3: Maggie, Rand Race and the rest are in Zimbodia to fix a rocket ship that landed in the jungle years before.

Hey Hopey: Siblings Hopey and Joey talk about their mother and Maggie.

On th' Road Ag'in: H. R. Costigan has hired Bomber to find Penny Century. When he comes across her by accident, she doesn't let him know who she is. Big 'Turo finally drags her back to Costigan's place. Later on, she flees again.

</Summary>
